                <td valign="top"><p><b><font size="5">My story</font>: November 11, 1999</b> -- If you've found this page you probably already know what 
                  relapsing polychondritis (RP) is. (If you don't know, you 
                  can read an article by Dr. Trentham, one of the foremost authorities 
                  on the subject, at <a href="http://rpolychondritis.tripod.com/DRTrentham.html" target="_blank">http://rpolychondritis.tripod.com/DRTrentham.html</a>. 
                  If you or someone you know suffers from a different autoimmune 
                  disease, read on: what helped me might also help others with 
                  related conditions.)</p>
