                    <tr align="center" bgcolor="#FFFFCC">
                      <td colspan="3"><p><b><font face="Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif" color="#CC0000">Update 
                          12/6/99</font></b>:<br>
                          <font face="Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif" size="-1">I 
                            spoke with RP expert Dr. Trentham today. <a href="update1.htm">Click 
                      here</a> to read about my call.</font></p>                        </td>
